283
00:24:35,500 --> 00:24:36,300
Your Majesty,

284
00:24:37,140 --> 00:24:38,300
if you like to have sweets,

285
00:24:38,420 --> 00:24:40,220
don't be too embarrassed to acknowledge it.

286
00:24:40,340 --> 00:24:41,420
There's nothing embarrassing

287
00:24:41,540 --> 00:24:42,980
that a man likes to have sweets.

288
00:24:46,700 --> 00:24:48,220
If I had sweets,

289
00:24:48,780 --> 00:24:50,100
I should like them.

290
00:24:50,980 --> 00:24:51,900
I've never seen my parents,

291
00:24:52,700 --> 00:24:54,940
