I may feel envious.

294
00:25:03,420 --> 00:25:04,740
Will you make sweets for me?

295
00:25:07,020 --> 00:25:08,740
I'll make sweets for you.

296
00:25:09,420 --> 00:25:11,020
I'm an expert at making sweets.

297
00:25:14,300 --> 00:25:15,300
When we come out,

298
00:25:15,820 --> 00:25:16,980
I'll take you home.

299
00:25:20,780 --> 00:25:22,220
I didn't feel homesick,

300
00:25:22,380 --> 00:25:23,700
since I forgot everything.

301
00:25:24,380 --> 00:25:25,620
But now I've been

302
00:25:25,780 --> 00:25:27,780
in the Dream of Aranya for a while.

303
00:25:28,940 --> 00:25:31,060
It has been long since I left Qingqiu.

304
00:25:32,180 --> 00:25:33,500
I feel homesick.

305
00:25:34,300 --> 00:25:36,900
Then we'll go back to Qingqiu first after we leave here.

306
00:25:40,700 --> 00:25:41,180
Well,

307
00:25:41,620 --> 00:25:42,540
Moye said

308
00:25:42,740 --> 00:25:44,820
if I want to leave the Dream of Aranya,

309
00:25:45,420 --> 00:25:47,900
I should go through Aranya's life

310
00:25:48,060 --> 00:25:49,540
as same as she did.

311
00:25:53,620 --> 00:25:55,340
It's fine that you do what he said.

312
00:25:55,900 --> 00:25:57,740
I'll take care of the rest.

313
00:26:19,300 --> 00:26:21,860
I know you prefer a quiet place,

314
00:26:22,100 --> 00:26:24,660
so I especially arrange the secluded Mengchun Courtyard for you.

315
00:26:25,340 --> 00:26:26,620
If you're not satisfied,

316
00:26:27,300 --> 00:26:30,100
there are other courtyards that can be arranged in the mansion.

317
00:26:30,860 --> 00:26:32,780
If you need anything,

318
00:26:33,100 --> 00:26:35,020
just instruct me.

319
00:26:41,060 --> 00:26:42,260
Hard to divert myself from troubles.

320
00:26:43,220 --> 00:26:44,460
Why so urgent?

321
00:26:45,300 --> 00:26:46,260
Life has diversity.

322
00:26:46,820 --> 00:26:48,060
Fate is sealed.

323
00:26:49,380 --> 00:26:50,580
Worry and horror

324
00:26:51,700 --> 00:26:53,140
will always come to an end.

325
00:26:54,180 --> 00:26:55,260
Her Highness usually likes to practice calligraphy.

326
00:26:55,900 --> 00:26:57,220
She always writes some inscriptions.

327
00:26:57,900 --> 00:26:59,500
It's the one Her Highness wrote in person.

328
00:27:00,300 --> 00:27:00,980
I know.

329
00:27:02,820 --> 00:27:04,020
I can recognize her handwriting.

330
00:27:07,860 --> 00:27:08,380
Let's go.

331
00:27:08,780 --> 00:27:09,420
Yes, Your Excellency.

332
00:28:48,060 --> 00:28:49,100
It's been two hundred years.

333
00:28:50,980 --> 00:28:52,620
We finally reach the last step

334
00:28:54,060 --> 00:28:55,620
after countless repetitions.

335
00:29:12,300 --> 00:29:14,820
Xiaobai looks almost the same as Aranya.

336
00:29:16,060 --> 00:29:18,460
Now Xiaobai's primordial spirit
comes to her own body spontaneously,

337
00:29:20,260 --> 00:29:22,540
which is really uncanny.

338
00:29:29,060 --> 00:29:31,420
Aranya's body is still in the Water Moon Pond.

339
00:29:57,620 --> 00:29:59,180
Xiaobai's primordial spirit comes to her own body

340
00:30:00,060 --> 00:30:01,940
while Aranya's body disappears.

341
00:30:03,900 --> 00:30:05,900
Does it mean Xiaobai replace Aranya?

342
00:30:07,980 --> 00:30:10,260
Aranya was born hundreds of years ago,

343
00:30:11,380 --> 00:30:14,020
