367
00:32:03,060 --> 00:32:04,500
They will confirmedly believe

368
00:32:04,980 --> 00:32:06,100
that you're Aranya.

369
00:32:07,780 --> 00:32:08,300
Xiaobai,

370
00:32:09,300 --> 00:32:10,940
there won't be any danger for you.

371
00:32:13,220 --> 00:32:13,700
Well,

372
00:32:13,940 --> 00:32:15,220
you exactly remind me.

373
00:32:15,460 --> 00:32:16,460
Shall I make a cut

374
00:32:16,580 --> 00:32:18,100
