385
00:32:54,300 --> 00:32:56,380
I was not stupid. I didn't act like that normally.

386
00:33:14,540 --> 00:33:15,900
I will only be away for a few days.

387
00:33:16,300 --> 00:33:17,100
You go back first.

388
00:33:18,940 --> 00:33:21,060
You should take good care of your wound.

389
00:33:27,100 --> 00:33:27,860
Behave yourself.

390
00:33:45,220 --> 00:33:46,300
Your Highness, you wake up.

391
00:33:47,220 --> 00:33:48,340
Do you feel well?

392
00:33:48,700 --> 00:33:49,980
Do you feel uncomfortable?

393
00:33:50,300 --> 00:33:51,860
Does your wound hurt?

394
00:33:52,500 --> 00:33:53,180
Chacha,

395
00:33:53,340 --> 00:33:53,820
you've asked so many questions,

396
00:33:53,980 --> 00:33:55,220
