397
00:33:55,660 --> 00:33:57,820
Yesterday Mr. Su said you were badly hurt and fainted away.

398
00:33:58,220 --> 00:33:59,900
I didn't know what was going on

399
00:34:00,060 --> 00:34:01,540
after Lord Xi Ze took you away.

400
00:34:01,700 --> 00:34:03,340
I was so worried about you.

401
00:34:03,660 --> 00:34:04,100
See,

402
00:34:04,700 --> 00:34:05,740
I'm fine.

403
00:34:09,020 --> 00:34:12,780
But why is your hand bandaged like this, Your Highness?

404
00:34:13,460 --> 00:34:15,020
It may be painful for a while.

405
00:34:16,580 --> 00:34:18,300
It's just a small wound. It doesn't matter.

406
00:34:18,700 --> 00:34:19,860
It'll be fine in a few days.

407
00:34:23,060 --> 00:34:23,740
Well, Your Highness,

408
00:34:24,100 --> 00:34:25,740
His Excellency Shen Ye moved to the mansion yesterday.

409
00:34:25,940 --> 00:34:28,140
The elder steward has arranged him in the Mengchun Courtyard.

410
00:34:28,660 --> 00:34:29,500
Is he satisfied?

411
00:34:30,460 --> 00:34:31,780
I heard from the elder steward that

412
00:34:31,980 --> 00:34:33,580
His Excellency Shen Ye seemed to know well

413
00:34:33,740 --> 00:34:35,540
of the environment in the mansion after he came here.

414
00:34:36,020 --> 00:34:37,860
He even didn't need the elder steward to lead the way for him.

415
00:34:38,220 --> 00:34:39,300
But I remember

416
00:34:39,460 --> 00:34:41,980
His Excellency Shen Ye has never been to our mansion.

417
00:34:44,620 --> 00:34:45,260
Is it true?

418
00:34:47,500 --> 00:34:48,700
He's a guest anyway.

419
00:34:48,940 --> 00:34:50,340
You take good care of him.

420
00:34:51,500 --> 00:34:52,460
Yes, Your Highness.

421
00:34:52,860 --> 00:34:54,180
Send him

422
00:34:54,500 --> 00:34:55,580
whatever he wants.

423
00:35:00,980 --> 00:35:02,340
What a good day today!

424
00:35:03,580 --> 00:35:03,980
Chacha,

425
00:35:04,500 --> 00:35:06,580
brew a pot of good tea and send it to the courtyard.

426
00:35:06,780 --> 00:35:08,260
Yes. I'm on my way.

427
00:35:13,140 --> 00:35:15,860
There're so many troubles in the Dream of Aranya,

428
00:35:16,940 --> 00:35:18,140
but His Majesty and I

429
00:35:18,500 --> 00:35:20,340
can live a peaceful life happily for a while

430
00:35:20,540 --> 00:35:21,380
in the name of

431
00:35:21,940 --> 00:35:23,860
Aranya and Lord Xi Ze's conjugal relation,

432
00:35:24,740 --> 00:35:26,700
which can be counted as a hard-won blessing.

433
00:35:35,940 --> 00:35:36,660
Your Highness,

434
00:35:37,780 --> 00:35:38,540
how is

435
00:35:40,220 --> 00:35:40,740
your wound?

436
00:35:41,140 --> 00:35:41,940
Moye,

437
00:35:42,180 --> 00:35:43,700
do you still think you didn't cheat me?

438
00:35:43,980 --> 00:35:44,540
See.

439
00:35:45,220 --> 00:35:46,580
I am almost killed

440
00:35:46,580 --> 00:35:48,300
by that white-fronted tiger.

441
00:35:48,420 --> 00:35:49,380
I'll definitely report to uncle

442
00:35:49,380 --> 00:35:50,420
about everything you've done to me when I leave here.

443
00:35:51,700 --> 00:35:54,220
I didn't expect that sacrificing your blood to the sword

444
00:35:54,620 --> 00:35:56,340
would make you hurt so heavily.

445
00:35:57,460 --> 00:35:59,860
Your Highness, I'm so sorry.

446
00:36:02,660 --> 00:36:03,500
I'm kidding.

447
00:36:03,860 --> 00:36:05,100
I'm lucky to have His Majesty by my side.

448
00:36:05,340 --> 00:36:06,620
He has healed me in time.

449
00:36:06,780 --> 00:36:08,140
I'm almost healed now.

450
00:36:09,340 --> 00:36:11,700
You get your memory back?

451
00:36:12,700 --> 00:36:15,020
That I am badly hurt this time
can be regarded as a blessing in disguise.

452
00:36:15,260 --> 00:36:16,820
Not only I get my memory back,

453
00:36:17,100 --> 00:36:18,660
but my primordial spirit also comes back to my body.

454
00:36:20,980 --> 00:36:21,820
What?

455
00:36:23,100 --> 00:36:23,580
This...

456
00:36:23,740 --> 00:36:24,700
