457
00:36:24,940 --> 00:36:25,620
Exactly.

458
00:36:25,980 --> 00:36:26,900
Now

459
00:36:26,940 --> 00:36:28,740
I'm the original Bai Fengjiu of Qingqiu.

460
00:36:30,740 --> 00:36:32,460
Aranya and you resemble each other too much.

461
00:36:33,020 --> 00:36:34,380
I can see no difference.

462
00:36:34,940 --> 00:36:35,660
Come here.

463
00:36:36,060 --> 00:36:37,620
Let me tell you the difference.

464
00:36:46,500 --> 00:36:46,940
See.

465
00:36:52,100 --> 00:36:53,260
There's no cut on your hand.

466
00:36:53,620 --> 00:36:55,500
Now do you believe me?

467
00:36:55,940 --> 00:36:56,460
Well,

468
00:36:56,820 --> 00:36:57,380
then

469
00:36:57,780 --> 00:36:59,300
where did you go yesterday?

470
00:36:59,700 --> 00:37:01,420
I didn't see you go back to Aranya's mansion,

471
00:37:01,740 --> 00:37:02,900
and I worried so much about your wound.

472
00:37:02,980 --> 00:37:04,140
I even went to the Qi Nan Palace,

473
00:37:04,540 --> 00:37:05,660
but I didn't find you there.

474
00:37:07,780 --> 00:37:09,540
It's a long story.

475
00:37:09,980 --> 00:37:11,260
When I woke up yesterday,

476
00:37:11,300 --> 00:37:12,980
I found myself lying at the side of Water Moon Pond.

477
00:37:13,380 --> 00:37:14,700
There's a freezing coffin right at the side of the pond.

478
00:37:14,900 --> 00:37:17,260
My original body was preserved in the freezing coffin.

479
00:37:17,500 --> 00:37:19,180
Once I touched my original body,

480
00:37:19,740 --> 00:37:20,860
my primordial spirit returned

481
00:37:20,900 --> 00:37:22,620
to my own body.

482
00:37:23,300 --> 00:37:24,860
And I got my memory back at the same time.

483
00:37:27,060 --> 00:37:29,060
What about Aranya's body?

484
00:37:31,300 --> 00:37:33,060
That's the strangest part

485
00:37:33,700 --> 00:37:36,540
that Aranya's body disappeared.

486
00:37:36,900 --> 00:37:38,220
Disappeared?

487
00:37:41,820 --> 00:37:42,820
How could it happen?

488
00:37:43,660 --> 00:37:44,740
I don't know.

489
00:37:47,140 --> 00:37:47,780
Well,

490
00:37:48,100 --> 00:37:48,860
Moye,

491
00:37:49,060 --> 00:37:49,860
you have asked me

492
00:37:50,100 --> 00:37:51,900
to invite Lord Shen Ye to the mansion, haven't you?

493
00:37:52,100 --> 00:37:53,540
Now he is in the mansion.

494
00:37:53,780 --> 00:37:55,260
What shall we do next?

495
00:37:55,900 --> 00:37:57,820
Aranya's body disappeared.

496
00:37:58,460 --> 00:37:59,340
How could it happen?

497
00:38:00,740 --> 00:38:01,580
Moye.

498
00:38:02,540 --> 00:38:03,740
Moye.

499
00:38:04,540 --> 00:38:05,580
What's wrong with you?

500
00:38:06,860 --> 00:38:07,740
Well,

501
00:38:09,100 --> 00:38:11,820
when Shen Ye lived in the mansion that year,

502
00:38:11,820 --> 00:38:12,780
he never stepped out of the side chamber

503
00:38:13,100 --> 00:38:14,580
because of his bad mood.

504
00:38:14,940 --> 00:38:16,380
Aranya wrote to him from time to time

505
00:38:16,780 --> 00:38:17,940
and talked with him,

506
00:38:18,260 --> 00:38:19,660
when she noticed it.

507
00:38:20,340 --> 00:38:22,100
Now I have to ask you

508
00:38:22,340 --> 00:38:23,660
to write some letters to Shen Ye

509
00:38:23,860 --> 00:38:25,900
in Aranya's handwriting.

510
00:38:27,220 --> 00:38:28,340
Are these letters the ones you showed me,

511
00:38:28,420 --> 00:38:29,420
when I just arrived here?

512
00:38:29,620 --> 00:38:30,380
Not exactly.

513
00:38:33,460 --> 00:38:36,140
Those letters are ones she wrote to me sometimes.

514
00:38:36,420 --> 00:38:39,340
These are ones she especially wrote to Shen Ye.

515
00:38:43,780 --> 00:38:46,260
But my handwriting isn't that good.

516
00:38:46,500 --> 00:38:47,980
If compared with Aranya's,

517
00:38:48,060 --> 00:38:49,500
mine will be far worse than Aranya's.

518
00:38:49,980 --> 00:38:52,540
You'll have to give me more time to practice my handwriting.

519
00:38:55,140 --> 00:38:56,100
Forget it. Forget it.

520
00:38:57,540 --> 00:38:59,260
You take good care of yourself first.

521
00:38:59,940 --> 00:39:02,420
I'll deal with the letter thing.

522
00:39:13,100 --> 00:39:13,860
Your Highness,

523
00:39:15,260 --> 00:39:16,300
do you think

524
00:39:17,020 --> 00:39:20,020
the Dream of Aranya is too bizarre?

525
00:39:20,620 --> 00:39:22,020
I'm even too bewitched to

526
00:39:22,380 --> 00:39:24,980
distinguish whether my feelings at the moment

527
00:39:26,100 --> 00:39:28,940
belong to me in the dream world

528
00:39:29,820 --> 00:39:31,860
or the original me in the real world,

529
00:39:32,580 --> 00:39:35,300
when I stay here for long.

530
00:39:41,700 --> 00:39:44,060
Your Highness, there's an ambiguous connection

531
00:39:44,060 --> 00:39:45,500
between Aranya and you.

532
00:39:46,060 --> 00:39:48,340
I'm afraid what's happening now is tricky.

533
00:39:48,540 --> 00:39:50,180
You'd better be careful.

534
00:39:54,300 --> 00:39:54,860
Moye,

535
00:39:55,700 --> 00:39:57,540
your feeling bewitched may be

536
00:39:57,940 --> 00:39:58,860
because the dream world

537
00:39:58,980 --> 00:40:00,540
