541
00:40:06,660 --> 00:40:07,980
you always care for Aranya.

542
00:40:08,380 --> 00:40:09,460
Perhaps you feel like this

543
00:40:10,580 --> 00:40:13,940
because of the devil inside.

544
00:40:15,100 --> 00:40:16,100
I don't feel the same as you,

545
00:40:16,420 --> 00:40:17,940
