546
00:40:18,260 --> 00:40:21,180
All that I care about is His Majesty.

547
00:40:21,460 --> 00:40:22,540
As long as His Majesty is here,

548
00:40:22,780 --> 00:40:24,460
I'll have nothing to worry about.

549
00:40:29,740 --> 00:40:31,220
I'm bewitched.

550
00:40:31,740 --> 00:40:33,460
Thank you for enlightening me, Your Highness.

551
00:40:33,780 --> 00:40:34,540
Not at all. Not at all.

552
00:40:35,300 --> 00:40:37,500
Moye, let's hasten

553
00:40:37,660 --> 00:40:39,300
to go through the whole life of Aranya.

554
00:40:39,620 --> 00:40:41,140
You can get the answer you want

